The Flash 114 (1996) (RoyalRumor-Novus) [NVS-D]


While pinballing through the timestream, Wally West runs into Don and Dawn Allen in the 30th century. Meanwhile, the new Polaris announces his presence, and Linda Park continues hanging out with the blue-clad Flash from the future. "Race Against Time" part 2.
